Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 那个机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太的乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜算多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用骷髅三号机收集的数据进行了模拟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大航速的话 我方占优
